{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"真的，你們喜愛現世的生活，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"而不顧後世的生活。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"在那日，許多面目是光華的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"是仰視著他們的主的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"在那日，許多面目是愁苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他們確信自己必遭大難。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"真的，靈魂達到鎖骨，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"有人說：「誰是祝由的？」"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他確信那是離別。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"（死時）脛與脛相纏結。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"在那日，他只被驅趕到你的主那裡。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"他沒有信道，也沒有禮拜。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"他否認真理，背棄正道，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"然後傲慢地走回家去。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"「毀滅已逐漸地臨近你。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"毀滅已逐漸地臨近你。」"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"難道人猜想自己是被放任的嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"難道他不曾是被射出精液嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"然後，他變成血塊，而真主加以創造他，使之成為肢體完全的人嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"他用精液造化兩性，男的和女的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"難道那樣的造化者不能使死人復活嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"人確實經歷一個時期，不是一件可以記念的事物。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我確已用混合的精液創造人，並加以試驗，將他創造成聰明的。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"我確已指引他正道，他或是感謝，或是辜負。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我確已為不信者預備許多鐵鏈、鐵圈和火獄。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"善人們必得飲含有樟腦的醴泉，"}]}